<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٤-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنِي عَبْدُ الْمَلِكِ الْمَيْمِونِيُّ وَالْحُسَيْنُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ الْأَنْمَاطِيُّ:</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَنَّهُمَا رَأَيَا أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ قَدْ خَضَبَ رَأْسَهُ وَلِحْيَتَهُ بِالْحِنَّاءِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٣١⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَالَ الْحُسَيْنُ:</span> خِضَابٌ قاني.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>